title: Diet Item Grouping
purpose: (Clinical Focus: These data elements support items that include food substances and enteral formula products to help a person meet macro- and micro-nutrient requirements.),(Data Element Scope: This template represents items  (ie, food substances and enteral formula products) that might be used as part of a Nutrition Order.),(Inclusion Criteria: Inclusion criteria include items (ie, food substances and enteral formula products) that might be used as part of a Nutrition Order.),(Exclusion Criteria: Parenteral nutrition products.)
